Bit/FlipFlop version 0.01
=========================

Bit::FlipFlop is a Perl5 module that facilitates the maintainence of
one bit (well perhaps slightly more) of state in a Perl program.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Perl5 and nothing more.

